    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a showroom-quality 2002 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine, equipped with individual throttle bodies and double VANOS variable valve timing. This specimen is paired with the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a factory M-variable differential lock for precise torque distribution. The chassis has undergone a rigorous inspection confirming zero subframe fatigue, and the suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications. Finished in Carbon Black Metallic, the paint depth is consistent across all panels, exhibiting no swirl marks or oxidation. The interior features Nappa leather with intact bolsters and fully functional electronics. This is a mechanically transparent, investment-grade example with a comprehensive service dossier.",
