    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that stands as a testament to meticulous ownership. This car is in showroom condition, having been strictly garage-kept and professionally detailed on a regular basis. The exterior paint is flawless, with a deep luster and no visible rock chips, scratches, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium leather seats show no bolster wear, the carpets are spotless, and all interior surfaces are free of any blemishes. Every feature, from the advanced infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control, operates perfectly. Mechanically, the vehicle is in top-tier form, supported by a complete, up-to-date service history from authorized technicians. It drives exactly as it did when new, offering a smooth, powerful, and rattle-free experience. This sale includes both original keys, all factory manuals, and a folder of maintenance records. For the discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection, this vehicle is ready for its next home.",
